  "text": "The use of molecular approach is also applied in the analysis of the antibiotic resistance of these isolates. In this sense, molecular detection of specific mutations in genes involved with drug resistance has successfully been applied in the identification of these (i.e. detection of mutations on rpoB, katG, mabA, etc.) [CITATION_1] .",
